    rdau:P61101 "<a href='https://www.darrellhowemortuary.com/obituaries/Charles-L-King?obId=29197353'>Darrell Howe Mortuaryn verkkosivut</a>, katsottu 3.9.2025 (Charles L. King, February 15, 1922 - March 6, 2017: ... Longtime Boulder resident Charles Lester King passed away March 6, 2017 at the MorningStar Assisted Living of Boulder. He was 95 years old. Charles Lester King was born February 15, 1922 in Gosford, California ... Charles received his Bachelor's degree at the University of New Mexico in 1948. He went on to earn his PhD from the University of Southern California in 1953. In 1964, Charles moved to Boulder. He was a professor of Spanish at CU in Boulder until his retirement in 1987.)"@fi,
