    rdau:P61101 "<a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heloise_Bowles_Cruse'>Wikipedia</a>, katsottu 11.9.2025 (Heloise Bowles Cruse (May 4, 1919 - December 28, 1977 was the original author of the popular syndicated newspaper column \"Hints from Heloise.\")"@fi,
        "<a href='https://recollections.biz/blog/heloises-1962-housekeeping-tips/'>Heloise's 1962 Housekeeping tips / Recollections</a>, katsottu 11.9.2025 (Texan Heloise Bowles was born in 1919 and her daughter, the current writer for the column, in 1951. Heloise Sr. began the column in 1959, making my book a real treasure, though it was already the third printing in 1962. ... Born none less than Ponce Kiah Marchelle Heloise Cruse Evans, Heloise Jr. took over the column when her mother passed in 1977.)"@fi,
